At this moment a small bot ran into the control room.  The bot 
halted as he saw the giant.  "Well......" he said, looking for words 
to speak to the enormous Skullhammer.  "uh...hi." he spit out 
finally.  He walked embarrased to his post by the communications 
and piloting.  "You wanna get to a Maximal base huh?  I could get 
you there.  It's not to far from here." he said as he hit some buttons 
bringing up a map over the center of the room.  "Pacifix, if I may."

--------------------------------------------------

Crotale senesed them entering the control room.  "Great idea chief, 
lets show him our heart." he said as he got up and walked ou 
towarsd the control room.
